Cyber Claw:




Cyber Claw stepped back as she saw Dinobot step towards her. She wondered 
how long this raptor would stay on the ground. She snarled loudly at him. 
"Keep that thing away from me before I rip it to shreds." she said.

She turned her head to Striker, saying, "Do you have authority over this 
issue?"
